cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.CR 

The paper discusses approaches for automatically assessing the credibility of information in social media, which involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.IR), and graph-based approaches (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the detection of opinion spam (cs.CR) and the credibility assessment of health-related information (cs.SI).
